# Secrets — never commit any of these.
# Full "don't commit" family (keep in sync with README "Privacy & logs" and docs/security.md):
#   .env                — API keys (OPENAI_API_KEY, ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, GITHUB_TOKEN, …)
#   credentials.json    — Google OAuth client secrets
#   token.json          — Google OAuth access/refresh tokens
#
# Four user-scoped artifacts (`.env`, `browser_profile/`, `auth_state.json`,
# `debug/`) live under ~/.brainchild/ now — the repo-root entries below are
# defensive only, for pre-migration checkouts or misconfigured environments.
.env
credentials.json
token.json
auth_state.json
browser_profile/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
dist/
build/
.venv/
venv/

# Claude Code memory
.claude/

# MCP server binaries
github-mcp-server

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Experiment logs (generated at runtime)
experiments/*/logs/

# Screenshots from test probes
/tmp/probe_*.png

# Internal planning docs
docs/agent-context.md
docs/roadmap.md
docs/product-strategy.md
docs/handoff.md
docs/decoupling_plan.md

# Debug reference logs
debug/model-log.md

# Runtime debug artifacts from MacOSAdapter session logging
debug/pre_camera_toggle.html
debug/pre_camera_toggle.png
